25:26.401 --> 25:28.028
What do you think you're right about?

25:29.321 --> 25:32.616
You wanna let me take you fishing,
but you're scared.

25:33.367 --> 25:35.911
I made a living reading fear
in people's eyes. I was a boxer.

25:36.662 --> 25:40.082
- What am I scared of?
- Getting knocked off your feet.

25:40.165 --> 25:42.876
Might take 12 rounds to get them
on their back, but I'm patient.

25:42.960 --> 25:44.253
Get me on my back?

25:44.837 --> 25:47.714
