into Christian faith

33:39.811 --> 33:41.730
by baptism, confirmation,

33:41.813 --> 33:43.106
and Eucharist.

33:43.190 --> 33:46.777
Stuart Long, what does
this period of formation offer you?

33:48.028 --> 33:49.238
Hard to say, Father.

33:49.321 --> 33:51.823
If I had to guess,
something beyond my wildest dreams.

33:51.907 --> 33:55.410
Let us all pray that in due time,
Stuart may be found worthy

33:55.494 --> 34:00.332
to receive the baptism of new birth,
the renewal in the Holy Spirit,

34:00.415 --> 34:02.209
and to complete his initiation

34:02.292 --> 34:05.838
through the sacraments
of confirmation and Eucharist.

34:07.089 --> 34:08.215
Hallelujah.

34:12.344 --> 34:14.554
I'd like to invite a friend
to sing with me.

34:16.598 --> 34:19.518
God gave you the talent.
It's a sin not to use it.

34:19.601 --> 34:21.812
- Give her a round of applause.
- Go.

34:21.895 --> 34:22.895
- Come on.
- Yeah.

34:25.815 --> 34:28.985
- Don't worry, I ain't gonna hurt you.
- What song?

34:29.777 --> 34:32.864
Damn, you smell good.
Hey, Johnny Cash, "Jackson."

34:33.907 --> 34:35.909
Read the words off the television.

35:25.042 --> 35:26.042
Oh, yeah.

35:36.011 --> 35:37.054
Yeah.

35:40.849 --> 35:45.312
For example, I am gonna give up chocolate.

35:45.395 --> 35:47.940
You should protest. She needs sweetening.

35:48.607 --> 35:50.150
Yeah, pick something else.

35:51.443 --> 35:53.987
