- Me?

35:57.741 --> 36:00.369
Maybe you guys,
so I can sleep in on Sundays.

36:00.452 --> 36:01.286
No.

36:01.370 --> 36:03.080
All right, all right.

36:05.207 --> 36:06.291
Alcohol.

36:06.875 --> 36:08.502
Hey, that's not fair.

36:08.585 --> 36:11.046
You pick something good
that you'll miss, to make it count.

36:11.129 --> 36:12.422
I like this kid.

36:14.174 --> 36:16.718
Like porn. That's what my dad gave up.

36:19.555 --> 36:22.391
Well, you tell him,
if he wants to make it count,

36:22.474 --> 36:24.309
tell your mama to give up sex.

36:24.393 --> 36:26.562
- He said S-E-X.
- That's what porn is.

36:26.645 --> 36:28.438
- Stu.
- Well, he said "porn."

36:28.522 --> 36:30.566
Kids, do you wanna read from...?

36:30.649 --> 36:32.150
- It's the same thing.
- No.

36:32.234 --> 36:33.902
Get your Bibles out, please.

36:35.863 --> 36:39.449
God wants us to give things up,
he ought to stop taking from us too.

36:39.533 --> 36:41.910
He killed my little brother Stephen
when he was 6.

36:41.994 --> 36:44.121
Took a nap, never woke up.

36:44.204 --> 36:45.873
How you square that one, huh?

36:46.915 --> 36:48.959
We can't understand
why God does what he does.

36:49.042 --> 36:52.212
That's why I liked to box.
How it went was up to me.

36:52.296 --> 36:54.631
I can't accept
when I ain't got no say in shit.

36:55.924 --> 36:59.845
Our world teaches us that there's comfort
in knowledge and fear in the unknown.

37:00.387 --> 37:03.515
What if the unknown was greater
than we could imagine?

37:04.057 --> 37:05.726
I bet it could be.

37:10.647 --> 37:11.815
I believe in you.

37:16.820 --> 37:17.820
<i>Confession.</i>

37:17.863 --> 37:22.117
Acknowledging our sins
in word, action, and omission,

37:22.201 --> 37:24.661
and resolving to not sin again.

37:24.745 --> 37:28.665
For this, we do penance,
and are granted forgiveness.

37:28.749 --> 37:31.502
Like doing laundry.
That's a Sunday thing too.

37:32.711 --> 37:34.880
Here I thought it'd be complicated.

37:34.963 --> 37:37.466
Well... I'm afraid it's not that simple.

37:37.549 --> 37:40.761
The essential part of penance

37:40.844 --> 37:43.055
is a firm and true repentance,

37:43.138 --> 37:44.806
motivated by faith,

37:44.890 --> 37:46.600
and the love of God.

37:46.683 --> 37:49.019
This is called perfect contrition.

37:49.102 --> 37:52.606
Imperfect contrition arises
from a less pure motive,

37:52.689 --> 37:54.525
such as common decency,

37:54.608 --> 37:55.859
or fear of hell.

37:55.943 --> 37:58.403
Our whole lives,
we're taught to be good, avoid bad.

37:58.487 --> 38:02.366
Eat your dinner, or you don't get dessert.
Share your toys, or you get timeout.

38:02.449 --> 38:04.785
