40:34.184 --> 40:35.561
What's everybody waiting for?

40:36.854 --> 40:38.105
Let's pray.

40:39.147 --> 40:39.982
I'll do it.

40:40.065 --> 40:41.275
It'd be my pleasure.

40:42.651 --> 40:43.902
I've been practicing.

40:59.376 --> 41:00.376
Amen.

41:03.422 --> 41:04.548
