42:21.542 --> 42:25.087
I am merely a vessel
to assist man in unburdening himself

42:25.170 --> 42:28.799
of all that may separate him
from the most direct path

42:28.882 --> 42:30.300
to Almighty Father.

42:30.384 --> 42:32.010
